<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #059669; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: white; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .success-box { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #059669; }
    .button { background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>âœ… Payment Confirmed!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.name || @user.email_address %>,</p>
      
      <div class="success-box">
        <h3>Great news! Your payment has been confirmed.</h3>
        <p>Your RepuTable account is now active and all services have been restored.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Payment Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Invoice: <%= @invoice.number %></li>
        <li>Amount: <%= @invoice.amount_formatted %></li>
        <li>Payment Date: <%= @invoice.paid_at&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
        <li>Method: Bank Transfer</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>What's next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your account access has been fully restored</li>
        <li>All campaigns and review collection are active</li>
        <li>Email notifications are enabled</li>
        <li>Next invoice will be generated at the end of your billing cycle</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.dashboard_url(host: 'reputable.co') %>" class="button">
          Access Dashboard
        </a>
      </p>
      
      <p>Thank you for your business! If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The RepuTable Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>RepuTable - Reputation Management Made Simple</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>